==儒格与美国射击队==
儒格有多年支持美国射击队的历史。他们不但直接提供资金支持，并且通过[[TALO_Distributors,_Inc.|TALO Distributors, Inc.]]<ref>[http://www.shotbusiness.com/Article/NewsBriefs/d1798b1d-5b63-46d8-a3d4-798602a2129b Ruger Raffle for USA Shooting Team - Article on Shotbusiness.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619153407/http://www.shotbusiness.com/Article/NewsBriefs/d1798b1d-5b63-46d8-a3d4-798602a2129b |date=2010-06-19 }}</ref>提供特殊型号。

